sun.jvm.hotspot.utilities.soql

Class MapScriptObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • sun.jvm.hotspot.utilities.soql.MapScriptObject
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ScriptObject
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    JSJavaScriptEngine

    public class MapScriptObject
extends java.lang.Object
implements ScriptObject
    Simple implementation of ScriptObject interface with property storage backed by a Map. This class can be extended to override any of the methods, in particular to add "function" valued properties.
